    "If the case is a class action matter (described below), this must also be included in the caption (Practical Law Litigation 2023a).",
    "• A jury demand if the plaintiff wants a jury to decide the case (Practical Law Litigation 2023a).",
    "• Various, specific sections in the body of the complaint:",
